        // CAP_PROP_CODEC_PIXEL_FORMAT =46,    //!< (read-only) codec's pixel format. 4-character code - see VideoWriter::fourcc . Subset of [AV_PIX_FMT_*](https://github.com/FFmpeg/FFmpeg/blob/master/libavcodec/raw.c) or -1 if unknown
